{"tid":2105534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我要為林鄭月娥講句公道話，其實佢心裡面係想泛民過半","createTime":"2020-07-12T16:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T17:04:59.000Z","uid":230104,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"711b3e20041daea84c9a2b4e969760d261f3ed06","tid":2105534,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:50:10.000Z","msg":"眾所鳩知，駱村官落左來之後，佢就變成左阿三，特區官員每日就一個個排隊入中聯辦面聖等指示，林鄭看在眼裡，心裡不是味兒<br />\n<br />\n而9月立法會選舉就係駱村長既DSE/成熟期，如果泛民過半，即駱村長初熟，可以燉，林鄭就用返絕技：打小報告，將個責任推得一乾二淨<br />\n<br />\n大家說對不對？"},{"pid":"b835db16438c7bdb456f0287abc086343f8a997c","tid":2105534,"uid":194120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:57:19.000Z","msg":"777只係傀儡"},{"pid":"2400a9fa74b14285eba0d86a3372854ccbce0cf9","tid":2105534,"uid":22609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"暗黑兵法救香港<br />\n用心良苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b0d2b54c57c515a3adfd66b2461d57fe6e4f29","tid":2105534,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"木木已成功將9月立法會選舉同駱村官仕途捆綁埋一齊，佢而家就等睇戲"}]}